#=GF RT   The MatP/matS site-specific system organizes the terminus region
#=GF RT   of the E. coli chromosome into a macrodomain. 
#=GF RA   Mercier R, Petit MA, Schbath S, Robin S, El Karoui M, Boccard F,
#=GF RA   Espeli O; 
#=GF RL   Cell. 2008;135:475-485.
